      <list id="id1171768178903" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>In Modules 1 and 2 you came into contact with art elements like <emphasis effect="bold">form</emphasis>, <emphasis effect="bold">line</emphasis>, <emphasis effect="bold">tone nuances</emphasis>, <emphasis effect="bold">colour</emphasis> and <emphasis effect="bold">composition</emphasis>.In Module 3 the emphasis is on <emphasis effect="bold">theme</emphasis>, <emphasis effect="bold">topic</emphasis> and <emphasis effect="bold">scale</emphasis> of work of art, at <emphasis effect="bold">home</emphasis>, in the <emphasis effect="bold">community</emphasis> and in <emphasis effect="bold">public places</emphasis>. </item>
      </list>
