      <para id="id4953322">STEP 2</para>
      <para id="id1171761129934">Study your completed table and <emphasis effect="bold">circle</emphasis> all the items that can be linked to decoration and then <emphasis effect="bold">underline</emphasis> all the items that have a SPECIFIC FUNCTION or which can be used for a specific purpose. Some items will meet with both requirements and will therefore be circled as well as underlined.</para>
